data.description:
Welcome home to this move-in-ready 3-bed, 2-bath beauty with updated flooring and carpet. This home comes with a 3 car garage which is perfect for extra storage. No HOA means freedom to customize!
Boasting a stunning mountain view, this property is perfect for those who appreciate natural beauty and serene surroundings.
Discover the perfect home featuring a water softener and paid-off solar panels for energy efficiency. Live comfortably and sustainably in this ideal abode.
